        <div class="divIntroColor">

            <div class="cocktails-div">

                <h1>Negroni Sbaglaito</h1>
                <img class="cocktail-images" src="Images/Negroni.webp" alt="Negroni">
                <div class="p-div-cocktail">
                    <p class="p-center">
                        The negroni sbagliato is basically a mistake negroni created by mistake .
                        <br>
                        The creator was busy speaking with a guest and instead of using gin he
                        accidentally poured Prosecco and serve it to the guest
                        <br>
                        The guest liked it and there you go negroni sbagliato is born.
                        <br>
                        The Sbagliato is nice to drink before dinner with classic aperitivo is bitter
                        sweet bubbly and has this little acidity of the prosecco
                        <br>
                        This is why is so loved isn't strong like
                        <a href="/negroni">Negroni</a>
                        and is a bit stronger than the
                        <a href="/americano">Americano</a>.
                        <br>
                        if you are interested to know more than check
                        <a class="link-text" href="/negroni-sbagliato-story">Here
                        </a>
                        .
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="cocktails-div">
                    <h2 >Method and preparation</h2>
                    <p class="p-center">
                        Mix vermouth and gin into the glass add some ice than gently add prosecco mix gently only one time using the spoon from bottom to the end  , stir it up and garnish
                        with a nice orange peel.
                        <br>
                    </p>
                    <p class="glass-p">
                        Glass: Tumbler
                        <br>
                        Method: Build
                        <br>
                        Garnish: Orange peel
                    </div>
                    <div class="div-ul">

                        <ul>
                            <li>3 cl Prosecco</li>
                            <li>3 cl Red Vermouth</li>
                            <li>3 cl Campari</li>
                        </ul>

                    </div>
                    <hr>

                </div>
            </div>

